<p class="note-body"><b>1990</b>—<plaw congress="101" isprivate="false" number="625">Pub. L. 101–625,</plaw> §801(a), amended section generally, substituting present provisions for provisions authorizing loans for housing and related facilities for elderly or handicapped families.</p>
