<p class="note-body">Subsec. (d)(9), (10). <plaw congress="100" isprivate="false" number="242">Pub. L. 100–242,</plaw> §162(b)(2), added pars. (9), (10).</p>
<p class="note-body">Subsec. (f). <plaw congress="100" isprivate="false" number="242">Pub. L. 100–242,</plaw> §162(c), designated existing provisions as par. (1) and added par. (2).</p>
<p class="note-body"><plaw congress="100" isprivate="false" number="242">Pub. L. 100–242,</plaw> §170(g)(2), substituted “section 133” for “section 134”.</p>
