<p class="note-body"><b>1983</b>—Subsec. (a)(3). <plaw congress="98" isprivate="false" number="181">Pub. L. 98–181,</plaw> §223(a)(1), inserted “, except that such interest rate plus such allowance shall not exceed 9.25 per centum per annum”.</p>
