<p class="note-body"><b>1979</b>—Subsec. (a)(4)(B)(i). <plaw congress="96" isprivate="false" number="153">Pub. L. 96–153,</plaw> §306(a), provided for increase of notes or other obligations to $3,827,500,000 on October 1, 1979, to $4,777,500,000 on October 1, 1980, and to $5,752,500,000 on October 1, 1981.</p>
