<p class="note-body">Subsec. (d)(1). <plaw congress="87" isprivate="false" number="723">Pub. L. 87–723,</plaw> §3(b)(1), redesignated subsec. (d)(1)(A) as entire subsec. (d)(1) and struck out subsec. (d)(1)(B) which included in definition of “housing” dwelling facilities provided by rehabilitation, alteration, conversion, or improvement of existing structures which were otherwise inadequate for proposed dwellings used by elderly families and persons.</p>
