<h4 class="note-head">Effective and Termination Dates of 1983 Amendment</h4>
<p class="note-body">Section 223(a)(2) of <plaw congress="98" isprivate="false" number="181">Pub. L. 98–181,</plaw> as amended by <plaw congress="99" isprivate="false" number="120">Pub. L. 99–120,</plaw> §5(b), Oct. 8, 1985, <statuteatlarge page="504" volume="99">99 Stat. 504</statuteatlarge>; <plaw congress="99" isprivate="false" number="156">Pub. L. 99–156,</plaw> §5(b), Nov. 15, 1985, <statuteatlarge page="817" volume="99">99 Stat. 817</statuteatlarge>; <plaw congress="99" isprivate="false" number="219">Pub. L. 99–219,</plaw> §5(b), Dec. 26, 1985, <statuteatlarge page="1732" volume="99">99 Stat. 1732</statuteatlarge>; <plaw congress="99" isprivate="false" number="267">Pub. L. 99–267,</plaw> §5(b), Mar. 27, 1986, <statuteatlarge page="75" volume="100">100 Stat. 75</statuteatlarge>; <plaw congress="99" isprivate="false" number="272">Pub. L. 99–272,</plaw> title III, §3011(b), Apr. 7, 1986, <statuteatlarge page="106" volume="100">100 Stat. 106</statuteatlarge>; <plaw congress="99" isprivate="false" number="289">Pub. L. 99–289,</plaw> §1(b), May 2, 1986, <statuteatlarge page="412" volume="100">100 Stat. 412</statuteatlarge>; <plaw congress="99" isprivate="false" number="345">Pub. L. 99–345,</plaw> §1, June 24, 1986, <statuteatlarge page="673" volume="100">100 Stat. 673</statuteatlarge>; <plaw congress="99" isprivate="false" number="430">Pub. L. 99–430,</plaw> Sept. 30, 1986, <statuteatlarge page="986" volume="100">100 Stat. 986</statuteatlarge>; <plaw congress="100" isprivate="false" number="122">Pub. L. 100–122,</plaw> §1, Sept. 30, 1987, <statuteatlarge page="793" volume="101">101 Stat. 793</statuteatlarge>; <plaw congress="100" isprivate="false" number="154">Pub. L. 100–154,</plaw> Nov. 5, 1987, <statuteatlarge page="890" volume="101">101 Stat. 890</statuteatlarge>; <plaw congress="100" isprivate="false" number="170">Pub. L. 100–170,</plaw> Nov. 17, 1987, <statuteatlarge page="914" volume="101">101 Stat. 914</statuteatlarge>; <plaw congress="100" isprivate="false" number="179">Pub. L. 100–179,</plaw> Dec. 3, 1987, <statuteatlarge page="1018" volume="101">101 Stat. 1018</statuteatlarge>; <plaw congress="100" isprivate="false" number="200">Pub. L. 100–200,</plaw> Dec. 21, 1987, <statuteatlarge page="1327" volume="101">101 Stat. 1327</statuteatlarge>, which provided that the amendment made by paragraph (1), amending this section, shall apply only with respect to loan agreements entered into after September 30, 1982, and not later than March 15, 1988, was repealed by <plaw congress="100" isprivate="false" number="242">Pub. L. 100–242,</plaw> title I, §161(c)(2), Feb. 5, 1988, <statuteatlarge page="1856" volume="101">101 Stat. 1856</statuteatlarge>.</p>
