<p class="note-body"><plaw congress="109" isprivate="false" number="163">Pub. L. 109–163,</plaw> div. A, title VI, §688(d), Jan. 6, 2006, <statuteatlarge page="3337" volume="119">119 Stat. 3337</statuteatlarge>, provided that: “The amendments made under subsection (a) [amending this section] shall take effect 150 days after the date of the enactment of this Act [Jan. 6, 2006].”</p>
