<p class="note-body"><plaw congress="109" isprivate="false" number="163">Pub. L. 109–163,</plaw> div. A, title VI, §688(b), Jan. 6, 2006, <statuteatlarge page="3337" volume="119">119 Stat. 3337</statuteatlarge>, provided that: “Nothing in this section [amending this section and enacting provisions set out as notes under this section] shall relieve any person of any obligation imposed by any other Federal, State, or local law.”</p>
