<p class="note-body"><plaw congress="109" isprivate="false" number="163">Pub. L. 109–163,</plaw> div. A, title VI, §688(c), Jan. 6, 2006, <statuteatlarge page="3337" volume="119">119 Stat. 3337</statuteatlarge>, provided that: “Not later than 150 days after the date of the enactment of this Act [Jan. 6, 2006], the Secretary of Housing and Urban Development shall issue a final disclosure form to fulfill the requirement of subclause (IV) of section 106(c)(5)(A)(ii) of the Housing and Urban Development Act of 1968 [<uscode detail="(c)(5)(A)(ii)(IV)" edition="2006" section="1701x" title="12">12 U.S.C. 1701x(c)(5)(A)(ii)(IV)</uscode>], as added by subsection (a).”</p>
