<h4 class="note-head">References in Text</h4>
<p class="note-body">The Housing Amendments of 1955, referred to in subsec. (f)(2), is act Aug. 11, 1955, ch. 783, <statuteatlarge page="635" volume="69">69 Stat. 635</statuteatlarge>, as amended. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title of 1955 Amendments note set out under <uscode edition="2006" section="1701" title="12">section 1701 of this title</uscode> and Tables.</p>
