<p class="note-body">Subsec. (b). <plaw congress="86" isprivate="false" number="372">Pub. L. 86–372,</plaw> §104(e)(1), struck out exceptions that related to housing for elderly persons from the two unnumbered paragraphs following par. (2).</p>
