<p class="note-body">Subsec. (f)(1). <plaw congress="98" isprivate="false" number="181">Pub. L. 98–181,</plaw> §434(1), struck out “the mortgagee is a public housing agency or an insured depository institution and” after “Where”. Notwithstanding the directory language that amendment be made to subsec. (g)(1), the amendment was executed to subsec. (f)(1) to reflect the probable intent of Congress and the intervening redesignation of subsec. (g) as (f) by <plaw congress="96" isprivate="false" number="470">Pub. L. 96–470</plaw>.</p>
