<p class="note-body"><b>1982</b>—Subsec. (d). <plaw congress="97" isprivate="false" number="289">Pub. L. 97–289</plaw> substituted “May 20, 1983” and “May 21, 1983” for “September 30, 1982” and “October 1, 1982”, respectively.</p>
