" number="345">Pub. L. 99–345,</plaw> §1, June 24, 1986, <statuteatlarge page="673" volume="100">100 Stat. 673</statuteatlarge>; <plaw congress="99" isprivate="false" number="430">Pub. L. 99–430,</plaw> Sept. 30, 1986, <statuteatlarge page="986" volume="100">100 Stat. 986</statuteatlarge>; <plaw congress="100" isprivate="false" number="122">Pub. L. 100–122,</plaw> §1, Sept. 30, 1987, <statuteatlarge page="793" volume="101">101 Stat. 793</statuteatlarge>; <plaw congress="100" isprivate="false" number="154">Pub. L. 100–154,</plaw> Nov. 5, 1987, <statuteatlarge page="890" volume="101">101 Stat. 890</statuteatlarge>; <plaw congress="100" isprivate="false" number="170">Pub. L. 100–170,</plaw> Nov. 17, 1987, <statuteatlarge page="914" volume="101">101 Stat. 914</statuteatlarge>; <plaw congress="100" isprivate="false" number="179">Pub. L. 100–179,</plaw> Dec. 3, 1987, <statuteatlarge page="1018" volume="101">101 Stat. 1018</statuteatlarge>; <plaw congress="100" isprivate="false" number="200">Pub. L. 100–200,</plaw> Dec. 21, 1987, <statuteatlarge page="1327" volume="101">101 Stat. 1327</statuteatlarge>; <plaw congress="100" isprivate="false" number="242">Pub. L. 100–242,</plaw> title IV, §§401(a)(4), 408(b), 415(b)(1), Feb. 5, 1988, <statuteatlarge page="1898" pages="1898, 1903, 1907" volume="101">101 Stat. 1898, 1903, 1907</statuteatlarge>; <plaw congress="107" isprivate="false" number="326">Pub. L. 107–326,</plaw> §3, Dec. 4, 2002, <statuteatlarge page="2793" volume="116">116 Stat. 2793</statuteatlarge>.)</p>
