<p class="note-body"><plaw congress="99" isprivate="false" number="120">Pub. L. 99–120</plaw> substituted “November 14, 1985” for “September 30, 1985”.</p>
<p class="note-body"><b>1983</b>—Subsec. (a). <plaw congress="98" isprivate="false" number="181">Pub. L. 98–181,</plaw> §441(a), inserted “or with monthly payments and outstanding balances adjusted by a percentage change in a selected price index” after “family income” and substituted “subsections (b) and (c) of this section” for “subsection (b) of this section”.</p>
