<p class="note-body"><b>1978</b>—<plaw congress="95" isprivate="false" number="630">Pub. L. 95–630</plaw> inserted “(1)” before “limiting the amount of interest” and “, or (2) requiring a minimum amortization of principal or otherwise relating to the amortization of principal under the mortgage or loan” after “payment mortgage provisions”.</p>
<!-- PDFPage:693 --><p class="note-body"><plaw congress="95" isprivate="false" number="557">Pub. L. 95–557</plaw> substituted “September 30, 1979” for “October 31, 1978”.</p>
