<p class="footnote"><a href="#1715z-13a_1" name="1715z-13a_1_target"><sup>1</sup> So in original. Probably should be section “3702(d)”.</a></p>
<!-- field-end:footnote -->
<!-- field-start:footnote -->
<p class="footnote"><a href="#1715z-13a_2" name="1715z-13a_2_target"><sup>2</sup> So in original. Probably should be “subsection (d) of this section”.</a></p>
<!-- field-end:footnote -->
<!-- field-start:footnote -->
<p class="footnote"><a href="#1715z-13a_3" name="1715z-13a_3_target"><sup>3</sup> So in original. The comma probably should not appear.</a></p>
