<h4 class="note-head">Prior Provisions</h4>
<p class="note-body">A prior section 810 of title VIII of act June 27, 1934, ch. 847, as added Sept. 1, 1951, ch. 378, title VI, §601(d), <statuteatlarge page="313" volume="65">65 Stat. 313</statuteatlarge>, which related to mortgage on housing constructed for personnel of the Atomic Energy Commission, was classified to section 1748g–1 of this title.</p>
