<p class="note-body">Section, act Sept. 28, 1951, ch. 434, title V, §505, <statuteatlarge page="365" volume="65">65 Stat. 365</statuteatlarge>, related to appropriation and expenditure of funds for acquisition of land, installation of outside utilities, and site preparation for housing projects constructed under this subchapter.</p>
