<!-- field-start:repealedhead -->
<h3 class="section-head">§§1749aa to 1749<em>ll</em>. Repealed. <plaw congress="101" isprivate="false" number="235">Pub. L. 101–235,</plaw> title I, §133(a), Dec. 15, 1989, <statuteatlarge page="2027" volume="103">103 Stat. 2027</statuteatlarge></h3>
<!-- field-end:repealedhead -->
<!-- field-start:repealsummary -->
<p class="note-body">Section 1749aa, act June 27, 1934, ch. 847, title X, §1001, as added Aug. 10, 1965, <plaw congress="89" isprivate="false" number="117">Pub. L. 89–117,</plaw> title II, §201(a), <statuteatlarge page="461" volume="79">79 Stat. 461</statuteatlarge>; amended Nov. 3, 1966, <plaw congress="89" isprivate="false" number="754">Pub. L. 89–754,</plaw> title X, §§1019, 1020(f), <statuteatlarge page="1295" pages="1295, 1296" volume="80">80 Stat. 1295, 1296</statuteatlarge>; May 25, 1967, <plaw congress="90" isprivate="false" number="19">Pub. L. 90–19,</plaw> §1(a)(3), <statuteatlarge page="17" volume="81">81 Stat. 17</statuteatlarge>, defined terms for this subchapter.</p>
